    "Data shaping ensures compatibility and consistency when sending data to models.",
    "Finally, we separated our data into training and testing sets.",
    "The training set is used to train our classification models so that they can learn and predict.",
    "The test set, which the models did not see during training, assesses their performance and generalization to new, previously unseen data.",
    "This methodical approach, from normalization to data conversion, reshaping, and splitting, lays the groundwork for successful classification model application to our dataset."
